## Networking

### Network Types

```bash
# Default bridge network
docker run --network bridge myapp

# Host network (no isolation)
docker run --network host myapp

# Custom network
docker network create mynetwork
docker run --network mynetwork myapp

# None (no networking)
docker run --network none myapp
```

### Container Communication

```yaml
# docker-compose.yml
services:
  app:
    networks:
      - backend
      - frontend

  api:
    networks:
      - backend

  db:
    networks:
      - backend

networks:
  frontend:
  backend:
```

```bash
# Containers on same network can use service name as hostname
# From 'app' container:
curl http://api:3000/health
psql -h db -U postgres
```

